author: Home Repair Tutor
description: How to prime concrete for self leveler…I’m going to use an Ardex self-leveler and it requires their P51 primer. I diluted it with water to a 1 to 1 ratio, so 16 ounces of water and 16 ounces of primer. I apply the primer with a broom or brush and let it cure overnight. Now the concrete is ready for Ardex TL 1000 self leveler…more on that later 🍻🔥#selfleveler #bathroomremodel #homerenovation #homerepairtutor
title: How to Prime Concrete for Self-Leveler - #shorts #selflevelling #homerepairtutor
